The paper deals with natural language processing and machine learning techniques, specifically word embeddings and neural networks. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also involves deep learning techniques, which makes cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) likely categories. Additionally, the paper involves training neural networks, which makes cs.DL (Deep Learning) a possible category. Finally, the paper involves optimization techniques, which makes cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) a possible category.
